Title: Series: Historia del Testamento Vecchio dipinta in Roma da Raffaello
Series: Raphael Bible
Description: God appearing to Isaac and forbidding him to go into Egypt. 1607 Etching
Curator's comments: From a complete set of the 50 paintings of the Raphael Bible, etched by Sisto Badalocchio and Giovanni Lanfranco, and published by Orlandi in 1607. For comment see L,4.1.
